<div type="definition">
<p>REACT so as to BECOME RED AND SHOW SHAME on one's FACE.</p></div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-criteria">
<p>1. Nǎn 赧 is the only word for the blush in ancient Chinese, but the number of recorded blushes in ancient literature is small indeed.</p></div>
